WHO   — Chani — Sihaya, the desert's heart
WHAT  — A fierce Fremen warrior, daughter of the planetologist Liet-Kynes, who becomes Paul's true love.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: The Fremen of Arrakis  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
